			Profile
			
			WelcometothepersonalwebsiteofChaoXuatZhejiangUniversity!
Dr.XureceivedhisB.Sc.degreeofmechanicalengineeringfromShenyangAerospaceUniversityin2002andhisM.Sc.degreeofmathematicsfromZhejiangUniversityin2005.HeobtainedhisPh.D.degreeofmechanicalengineeringfromLehighUniversityin2010.
ChaoXuiscurrentlytheTRUTHAssociateProfessorofapplieddynamics&amp;controlintheInstituteofCyber-SystemsandControl.HealsoservesasCo-Managing-EditorinJournalofIndustrialandManagementOptimization(JIMO).
Youmayfindmoreinformationbybrowsingthemenuontheright.Enjoyexploringthissite!&nbsp;

